
---

## Auth
```
POST /api/v1/auth/login
POST /api/v1/auth/verify-otp
POST /api/v1/auth/register
POST /api/v1/auth/logout
```

## Marchés
```
GET  /api/v1/marches
GET  /api/v1/marches/{id}
GET  /api/v1/marches/{id}/cdc        (file download)
GET  /api/v1/marches/{id}/questions
POST /api/v1/marches/{id}/questions
```

## Soumissions
```
GET      /api/v1/soumissions/mes-soumissions
GET      /api/v1/soumissions/{id}/notes
POST     /api/v1/soumissions/{marcheId}/enveloppe-admin      (multipart)
POST     /api/v1/soumissions/{marcheId}/enveloppe-technique  (multipart)
POST     /api/v1/soumissions/{marcheId}/enveloppe-financiere (multipart)
POST     /api/v1/soumissions/{marcheId}/confirmer
```

## Recours & Notifications
```
POST /api/v1/recours
GET  /api/v1/notifications
PUT  /api/v1/notifications/{id}/lire
PUT  /api/v1/notifications/lire-toutes
```

## IA
```
POST /api/v1/ia/valider-dossier-admin
POST /api/v1/ia/estimation-prix/{marcheId}

